{"tha-ap62:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap62:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap62:0.3":"Asanabodhiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap62:1.1":"“Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap62:1.2":"addasam lokanayakam; ","tha-ap62:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap62:1.4":"upagacchim naruttamam. ","tha-ap62:2.1":"Tissassaham bhagavato, ","tha-ap62:2.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap62:2.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap62:2.4":"ropayim bodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap62:3.1":"Asano namadheyyena, ","tha-ap62:3.2":"dharaniruhapadapo; ","tha-ap62:3.3":"Pancavasse paricarim, ","tha-ap62:3.4":"asanam bodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap62:4.1":"Pupphitam padapam disva, ","tha-ap62:4.2":"abbhutam lomahamsanam; ","tha-ap62:4.3":"Sakam kammam pakittento, ","tha-ap62:4.4":"buddhasettham upagamim. ","tha-ap62:5.1":"Tisso tada so sambuddho, ","tha-ap62:5.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap62:5.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap62:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap62:6.1":"‘Yenayam ropita bodhi, ","tha-ap62:6.2":"buddhapuja ca sakkata; ","tha-ap62:6.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap62:6.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap62:7.1":"Timsakappani devesu, ","tha-ap62:7.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap62:7.3":"Catusatthi cakkhattum so, ","tha-ap62:7.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap62:8.1":"Tusita hi cavitvana, ","tha-ap62:8.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap62:8.3":"Dve sampatti anubhotva, ","tha-ap62:8.4":"manussatte ramissati. ","tha-ap62:9.1":"Padhanapahitatto so, ","tha-ap62:9.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap62:9.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap62:9.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap62:10.1":"Vivekamanuyuttoham, ","tha-ap62:10.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap62:10.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap62:10.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap62:11.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap62:11.2":"bodhim ropesaham tada; ","tha-ap62:11.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap62:11.4":"bodhiropassidam phalam. ","tha-ap62:12.1":"Catusattatito kappe, ","tha-ap62:12.2":"dandasenoti vissuto; ","tha-ap62:12.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap62:12.4":"cakkavatti tada ahum. ","tha-ap62:13.1":"Tesattatimhito kappe, ","tha-ap62:13.2":"sattahesum mahipati; ","tha-ap62:13.3":"Samantaneminamena, ","tha-ap62:13.4":"rajano cakkavattino. ","tha-ap62:14.1":"Pannavisatito kappe, ","tha-ap62:14.2":"punnako nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap62:14.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap62:14.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap62:15.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap62:15.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap62:15.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap62:16.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma asanabodhiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap62:17.1":"Asanabodhiyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap62:18.1":"Bijanivaggo chattho. ","tha-ap62:19.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap62:20.1":"Bijani sataramsi ca, ","tha-ap62:20.2":"sayanodakivahiyo; ","tha-ap62:20.3":"Parivaro padipanca, ","tha-ap62:20.4":"dhajo padumapujako; ","tha-ap62:20.5":"Bodhi ca dasamo vutto, ","tha-ap62:20.6":"gatha dvenavuti tatha. "}